  "body": "Zone file reload is currently \"hardcoded\" to 1 minute https://github.com/coredns/coredns/blob/master/plugin/file/reload.go#L9\r\nIn some cases (like more complex provisioning) this is too long time. This can be also seen in tests when reload time is \"hacked\" to 15 seconds.\r\nAlternative is sending SIGUSR1 signal, but this seems to reload all modules, drop caches and is quite heavy.\r\n\r\nBest way of improving this would be to watch on inotify on config files and apply changes as soon as they appear i n zone file.\r\nEasier way, that can be implemented faster, is to expose reload time in plugin setup.",
